name: Colourful Cthulhu
description:
My inaugural, commemorative work to celebrate the debut of My new collection, “Lovecraftian Flora, Floral, Fruitful, and Fungal Horrors,” which consists of four ongoing series that will grow over time. In this piece, Lovecraft's most famous character is rendered as an unholy merger of tropical flowers and cosmic horror.

This edition of 40 was given away via airdrop to top collectors of Mine, friends, people who have been kind to Me, and a few artists I admire.

Two artificial intelligence systems (VQGAN+CLIP) created this work. No input image was used.

2752x2752 pixel PNG

Minted December 11th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or vqgan.tormential.tez
